These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, juice, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, american, polish, chinese
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
2. the chinese is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the malaysian is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
5. the malaysian is the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking juice is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola  | soy-milk | fanta  | juice |
| Nationality   | polish | chinese      | malaysian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, mexican, canadian, american
4 different pets are kept: snake, pony, guinea-pig, turtle
1. the mexican is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the american##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | canadian | mexican   | colombian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig      | snake    | pony | turtle      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, raspberry, radish, grapes
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, motorbike, taxi
1. the person eating raspberry is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
6. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | raspberry | kale | radish     | grapes |
| Transport   | scooter  | taxi   | motorbike | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, hiking, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel, action, musical
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
4. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
5. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | traveling | gardening | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | action     | time-travel    | adventure       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, radish, plum, cranberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, time-travel, adventure
1. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
2. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
3. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
6. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | plum | cranberry   | orange   | radish    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | adventure | animation | time-travel |

