.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, lawyer, teacher, journalist
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, polish, french, german
1. the journalist is in an odd position##4
2. the coach is somewhere to the left of the german##5
3. the german is between the journalist and the french##2
4. the teacher is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | coach | lawyer | journalist | teacher |
| Nationality   | french        | german     | indian       | polish   |

