.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, dubstep, folk, classical
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, chinchilla, dog
1. the owner of the cat is the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of indie is between the fan of dubstep and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
5. the fan of indie is in an even position##4
6. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | indie  | folk  | classical   |
| Pet           | dog  | rabbit | chinchilla | cat |

