.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, pomegranate, lettuce, banana
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, bartender, dressmaker
1. the lawyer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the analyst##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | pomegranate     | banana | lettuce     | lime   |
| Job    | dressmaker | lawyer  | bartender | analyst |

