.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, soy-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, pepper, cherry, corn
1. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
5. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
6. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating cherry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | tea   | lemonade |
| Food       | cauliflower       | cherry   | corn | pepper |

