.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, lemonade, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, skiing, basketball
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
3. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
4. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
5. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | juice | lemonade       | water   | soy-milk        |
| Sport      | cycling  | basketball | baseball | skiing |

