.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, singing, card-games, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, baseball, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | reading | singing   | card-games | skydiving     |
| Sport   | skateboarding     | weightlifting | baseball  | volleyball |

