.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, western, adventure, zombie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, parkour, baseball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the person watching satire movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | adventure        | zombie        | western |
| Sport         | baseball  | sailing | cricket | parkour |

