1. the fan of r&b is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
3. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
5. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | cooking | singing | filmmaking | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | techno  | r&b  | jazz    |

