.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, sudoku, rock-climbing, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, chef, journalist, pilot
1. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
2. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
5. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
6. the journalist is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | cooking | rock-climbing  | reading      | sudoku |
| Job     | journalist    | pilot | chef | librarian   |

