.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, punk, salsa, techno
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking coffee and the fan of punk##2
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk      | almond-milk       |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | techno | punk | d&b |

