The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike, jet-ski, motorbike
1. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
2. the canadian is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the british##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | british     | argentine | colombian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike | quad-bike    | jet-ski    | motorbike |

