.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, water, mirinda
There are 4 different nationalities: american, colombian, japanese, canadian
1. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3
2. the american is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
3. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the american is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
5. the american is on the left of the colombian##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking mirinda and the colombian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | water     | mirinda | iced-tea     | coffee |
| Nationality   | japanese | canadian  | american | colombian        |

