.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, fish, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, airplane, car, tram
1. the owner of the horse is between the person driving the airplane and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
2. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | fish   | snake   | horse       | guinea-pig   |
| Transport   | car | airplane | trike | tram |

