.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, pepper, pomegranate, bikerot
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, van, boat
1. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
2. the person eating onion is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
6. the person eating onion is between the person eating bikerot and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | pepper     | bikerot | onion | pomegranate |
| Transport   | van | boat | motorbike      | bike        |

 